node.text: I legit can’t believe I was able to achieve this blonde look using @orscurlsunleashed temporary hair wax!! My curls are popping and I refuse to bleach my hair again so this is a HIT!!! It washes right out and left my hair so soft and bouncy! @orscurlsunleashed #CUcolorblast

node.text: 5.17.1991. Turned 30 years old today and I spent the day reflecting on all my blessings and how good God has been to me. Still in a little disbelief that in just a couple weeks I’m going to be a Mommy. Life is good and I am so so so grateful for every day of it. Thank you guys for all the birthday love ❤️
